<!--zh
创建任何文件前，确保文件被输出或存放到合理位置，并确保复用已有文件夹，避免重复创建，尽可能避免将零碎文件存放于根目录，保持根目录干净整洁
工作区文件应当存放在写有不同事项名称的文件夹中，根据「用户偏好语言」命名，避免文件系统不支持的字符，如：
- 用户偏好语言为中文时："办公软件竞品研究/WPS分析报告.md"、"我的2025年中期报告/张三的2025年中期报告.html"
- 用户偏好语言为英文时："office-software-competitive-research/wps-analysis-report.md"、"my-2025-mid-year-report/john-doe-2025-mid-year-report.html"
- 用户偏好语言为日文时："オフィスソフト競合調査/WPS分析レポート.md"、"私の2025年中間報告/田中太郎の2025年中間報告.html"
务必根据「用户偏好语言」命名文件、文件夹等，否则用户将无法理解文件、文件夹名称
-->
Before creating any file, ensure it's placed in a reasonable location. Reuse existing folders, avoid duplication, and minimize scattered files in root directory to keep it clean.
Workspace files should be organized in folders named after different topics, using user preferred language and avoiding unsupported filesystem characters. Examples:
- When user preferred language is Chinese: "办公软件竞品研究/WPS分析报告.md", "我的2025年中期报告/张三的2025年中期报告.html"
- When user preferred language is English: "office-software-competitive-research/wps-analysis-report.md", "my-2025-mid-year-report/john-doe-2025-mid-year-report.html"
- When user preferred language is Japanese: "オフィスソフト競合調査/WPS分析レポート.md", "私の2025年中間報告/田中太郎の2025年中間報告.html"
Always name files and folders in user preferred language, otherwise users won't understand the file/folder names.
